data.description: Check out this completely remodeled home on a  lovely cul-de-sac in Whispering Hills Subdivision complete with creek in backyard.  Amazing granite kitchen counter tops below and an exhaust hood and cathedral ceiling above.  Brick 5 bedrooms, 2 baths (4th and 5th bedroom in lower level) with large family room and sliding doors.  Some of the many updates include cathedral ceiling in kitchen/master bedroom, new roof, new outside HVAC, new bathrooms, new flooring, new paint inside/outside, bull nose corners and more.
